description: This common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 34, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 102, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 2 for East, Leverage for South, and 3 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [102 Votes, Common]
